far less influence over Trump than <strong>Elon Musk</strong>,<strong></str=
ong>who has his own stake in the outcome as the owner of X, a rival social =
platform whose financial viability at the moment seems to be
dependent on Musk continuing to personally make billion-dollar annual inter=
est payments, as my partner <strong>Bill Cohan</strong> recently <a href=3D=
"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dUc3=
