036701a95554bc9e31" style=3D"text-decoration:underline;color:#d40000;">cove=
red</a> this dispute a few months ago: Young, a military vet, helped evacua=
te Afghans fleeing the Taliban, only to find himself featured in a CNN segm=
ent about =E2=80=9Cblack markets=E2=80=9D in Afghanistan that were allegedl=
